T16TD4349E:161b-1: by'a ka ra na lingg'a ba t'a ra na n'a ma /
T16TD4349E:161b-3: lung du ston pa rtags kyi 'jug pa zhes bya ba /

T16TD4349E:161b-6: thams cad mkhyen la phyag 'tshal lo //
T16TD4349E:161b-7: pho yi yi ge 'ba' zhig la //

T16TD4349E:161b-13: / sde pa bzhi pa yan chad dbye //

T16TD4349E:161b-16: wa ni ba dang sbyar bar bya //
T16TD4349E:161b-17: lhag ma drug ni mo ru sbyar //

T16TD4349E:161b-22: 'jug pa bcu yi nang nas ni //
T16TD4349E:161b-23: sngon 'jug yi ge lnga dbyung bya //
T16TD4349E:161b-24: sngon 'jug yi ge lnga po la //

T16TD4349E:162a-0: pho ni pho dang mo la @162a * //
T16TD4349E:162a-1: 'jug / mo ni mo dang ma ning la //
T16TD4349E:162a-2: ma ning yang ni pho mo la'o //
T16TD4349E:162a-3: shin tu mo ni ma ning dang //
T16TD4349E:162a-4: mo dang shin tu mo nyid la'o //
T16TD4349E:162a-6: pho ni ma ning la mi 'jug / mo ni pho la 'jug pa min //
T16TD4349E:162a-7: ma ning rang la rang mi 'jug / rang gi sde dang phrad pa na //
T16TD4349E:162a-9: ma ning mo yang de bzhin no //
T16TD4349E:162a-10: ji ltar 'jug par byed ce na //
T16TD4349E:162a-11: pho ni drag po'i tshul gyis 'jug / ma ning ran par 'jug pa yin //
T16TD4349E:162a-12: mo ni zhan pa'i tshul gyis 'jug / shin tu mo ni mnyam pas so //
T16TD4349E:162a-13: ci phyir 'jug par byed ce na //
T16TD4349E:162a-14: pho ni 'das dang gzhan bsgrub phyir //
T16TD4349E:162a-15: ma ning gnyis ka da ltar ched //
T16TD4349E:162a-16: mo ni bdag dang ma 'ongs phyir //
T16TD4349E:162a-17: shin tu mo ni mnyam phyir ro //
T16TD4349E:162a-18: rjes 'jug yi ge bcu po la //
T16TD4349E:162a-19: pho mo ma ning gsum du dbye //
T16TD4349E:162a-20: pho la skyes bu rab 'bring gsum //
T16TD4349E:162a-21: mo la mo dang shin tu mo //
T16TD4349E:162a-22: ma ning 'gyur dang mtshan gnyis dang //
T16TD4349E:162a-23: mtshan med dag dang gsum du 'dod //
T16TD4349E:162a-24: de yang byed pa bzhi bzhi ste //
T16TD4349E:162a-25: gang la 'jug byed gang gis byed //
T16TD4349E:162a-26: ji ltar byed dang ci phyir byed //
T16TD4349E:162a-27: gang la yi ge thams cad la //
T16TD4349E:162a-28: gang gis bcu po de dag gis //
T16TD4349E:162a-29: ji ltar rnam pa gnyis yin te //
T16TD4349E:162a-30: sgra yi 'jug tshul don gyi tshul //
T16TD4349E:162a-31: pho gsum mo gnyis ma ning gsum //
T16TD4349E:162a-32: drag zhan bar ma gsum du 'jug / drag pa gsum ni nang phrad dam //
T16TD4349E:162a-33: gal te zhan pa nang phrad na //
T16TD4349E:162a-34: de la nang gi cha shas kyis //
T16TD4349E:162a-35: de yang drag zhan gnyis su dbye //
T16TD4349E:162a-36: ma ning gsum du gang gtogs pa //
T16TD4349E:162a-37: drag dang phrad na drag par 'gyur //
T16TD4349E:162a-38: zhan dang phrad na zhan par 'gyur //
T16TD4349E:162a-39: gnyis ka dag dang phrad gyur na //
T16TD4349E:162a-40: de ni gnyis ka can du 'gyur //
T16TD4349E:162a-41: gnyis ka dag dang ma phrad na //
T16TD4349E:162a-42: gang du yang ni mi 'gyur ro //
T16TD4349E:162a-43: des na 'gyur dang mtshan gnyis dang //
T16TD4349E:162a-44: mtshan med ma ning gsum du 'dod //
T16TD4349E:162a-45: de ni sgra yi 'jug tshul lo //
T16TD4349E:162a-46: don gyi rnam pa gnyis yin te //
T16TD4349E:162a-47: snga ma gang ltar gyur pa dang //
T16TD4349E:162a-48: phyi ma gang ltar gyur pa'o //
T16TD4349E:162a-49: snga ma sngon 'jug sngar bzhin sbyar //
T16TD4349E:162a-50: phyi ma dag gi 'dren tshul ni //
T16TD4349E:162a-51: pho yis pho yi ming mtha' drang //
T16TD4349E:162a-52: mo yis mo yi ming mtha' drang //
T16TD4349E:162a-53: ma ning gis ni ma ning ngo //
T16TD4349E:162a-54: ming mtha' de dag nyid kyis ni //
T16TD4349E:162a-55: de nyid rang gi sgra mthun pa'i //
T16TD4349E:162a-56: chos dngos las dang byed pa dang //
T16TD4349E:162b-1: gnas dang bod pa'i sgra yang drang //
T16TD4349E:162b-2: gzhan yang slar bsdu lhag bcas dang //
T16TD4349E:162b-3: 'byed sdud bsnan dang bdag po dang //
T16TD4349E:162b-4: dgag sgrub rgyan dang dus la 'jug / de dag snga shugs 'dren pas 'byung //
T16TD4349E:162b-5: de dag nang gses gang 'jug pa //
T16TD4349E:162b-6: mtha' sbyar 'og ma'i ming don las //
T16TD4349E:162b-7: spyir 'jug yod dam byed pa yod //
T16TD4349E:162b-8: de bzhin ched byed rten byed dang //
T16TD4349E:162b-9: las bya blang bya bsgrub par bya //
T16TD4349E:162b-11: gzhan yang tshig don 'og ma las //
T16TD4349E:162b-12: bsdu rgyu yod dam med pa dang //
T16TD4349E:162b-13: gong ma las kyang de bzhin te //
T16TD4349E:162b-14: rnam grangs dag ni bkod pa las //
T16TD4349E:162b-15: bskyar ba yod dam med pa dang //
T16TD4349E:162b-16: pho sgra dang ni mo sgra dag / ming gi mtha' la yod med dang //
T16TD4349E:162b-17: rgyan du gyur pa rnams la yang //
T16TD4349E:162b-18: don la snyegs pa yod med dang //
T16TD4349E:162b-19: bstan bya lhag ma yod med dang //
T16TD4349E:162b-20: tshig don rdzogs dang ma rdzogs kyis //
T16TD4349E:162b-21: de dag nang gses rnam bar dbye //
T16TD4349E:162b-22: ci phyir 'jug par byed ce na //
T16TD4349E:162b-23: yi ge'i khong nas ming dbyung ste //
T16TD4349E:162b-24: ming gi khong nas tshig phyung nas //
T16TD4349E:162b-25: tshig gis don rnams ston byed pa'o //
T16TD4349E:162b-26: mo yi yi ge med pa na //
T16TD4349E:162b-27: pho yig brjod pa med par 'gyur //
T16TD4349E:162b-28: pho yig de dag rnams la yang //
T16TD4349E:162b-29: 'jug par bcas pa med na ni //
T16TD4349E:162b-30: ming dang tshig kyang gsal mi nus //
T16TD4349E:162b-31: ming tshig gsal ba med na ni //
T16TD4349E:162b-32: don rnams brjod par mi 'gyur ro //
T16TD4349E:162b-33: de ltar gyur na 'jig rten na //
T16TD4349E:162b-34: don mtshan brjod pa kun kyang med //
T16TD4349E:162b-35: rig byed smra ba'ang yod mi 'gyur //
T16TD4349E:162b-36: nyan thos rang rgyal sangs rgyas kyi //
T16TD4349E:162b-37: bslab pa rnams kyang med par 'gyur //
T16TD4349E:162b-38: ji ltar 'jig rten sems can dag / phung po khams dang skye mched dang //
T16TD4349E:162b-39: grub mtha' gzhan yang yod mod na'ang //
T16TD4349E:162b-40: rang nyid kyis ni mi shes bzhin //
T16TD4349E:162b-41: de bzhin yi ge'i 'jug tshul rnams //
T16TD4349E:162b-42: smra ba rnams la gnas gyur kyang //
T16TD4349E:162b-43: rang tshul de nyid mi shes pas //
T16TD4349E:162b-44: don la sbyor ba ga la shes //
T16TD4349E:162b-45: de phyir smra ba'i skyes mchog gis //
T16TD4349E:162b-46: rjes smras 'di kun rtogs gyur cig / lung du ston pa rtags kyi 'jug pa zhes bya ba slob dpon aa nus mdzad pa'o /
